% if ($cluster->getName eq 'ORF Prediction'){
<p>Glimmer3 is run iteratively to produce more accurate start-site predictions. 
We run Glimmer3 first without a PWM, generating a set of gene predictions. Then extracting 
regions upstream of those predictions as input to <a class="normal" href="http://cbcb.umd.edu/software/ELPH/">
ELPH</a> to produce a PWM. We re-run Glimmer3 using the PWM to produce a more accurate set 
of start-site predictions.  Please see this <a class="normal" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17237039">
article</a> for a more detailed description.</p>

% }

